Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:06.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:22.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:23.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:27.91,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:29.38,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:36.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather will come\nfluttering down, swaying gently in the\nair.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:43.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.63,0:00:53.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:59.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as l've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:06.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:13.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:21.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:26.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:04.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,O Light of Protection,\nI summon you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:06.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Create a protective wall around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:09.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Immortal Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.89,0:02:24.35,AMG episode name red,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! Always By Your Side...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:29.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're safe now, since he\nwon't be able to come inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:32.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But why is Midgard attacking us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:36.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was a good nap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:38.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the commotion, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:40.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:43.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! You're back to\nnormal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:44.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:48.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you break your power limiter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:52.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Almighty said he'd\nlet it go just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:56.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And look at all this...\nwhat in the world happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:59.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:02.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:03.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:06.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The reason the amusement park's\na mess and the sky's so dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:11.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and the whole city's in an uproar...\nall that, all that, all that is your fault,\NUrd!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:13.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, but I don't remember a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:17.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd say about half of it is my fault.{\i0}\NMaybe, but I don't remember a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:20.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Midgard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:22.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So is your emotional reunion over yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:24.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is that giant snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am not Midgard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:28.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:34.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Lord of Terror and I am also\nthe Ultimate Destruction Program.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:36.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...he got infected?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:39.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so the program's\nself-replicating...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:43.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...I don't have\nany idea what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:48.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the vaccine\ndeletes the host program...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:53.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it can still survive by self-replicating\nand sneaking into another file.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:59.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, what I want to know is\nwhat happened before all of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:01.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:06.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So long as I continue to self-reproduce,\nno one will ever destroy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:10.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:22.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Gate of the Netherworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:27.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's the gate connecting\nthis world to the world of the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:30.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure the Almighty sealed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:36.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But once I've breached that cursed seal,\nwhat do you suppose will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:39.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The demons will be coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:41.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:46.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We demons will be able to infiltrate\nthis world without a catalyst!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:52.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It will truly become\na world of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:56.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can you imagine how easy it will be to\nincrease our dominance here on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:01.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:04.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...I want you\nto take down the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:08.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are,\nand what happened here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:13.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but the one thing I know is that\nyou tried to harm my precious sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:16.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The hell with my license suspension!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:19.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to strike him down myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Descend, Exploding Thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:25.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:29.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He drained all of your power\nbefore you woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:30.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:36.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A creature like that...he's not\nworthy of being smited by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:39.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld! Take him out right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:40.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:44.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man! What choice do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:48.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:53.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, look at him burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:56.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Skuld...got anything else to toss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:02.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you cry...\nI'll make you scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:13.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's not that different now than\nwhen she was the Lord of Terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:15.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:16.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:22.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If he just wants to break the seal,\nhe could just do it in secret somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.87,0:06:25.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\nyou're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's another thing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:30.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones standing in his way...\nbut he's not attacking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:35.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that he needs some kind\nof power in order to break the seal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:36.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:40.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Skuld, isn't there\nany way to delete him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:43.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you read the instruction\nmanual for the flute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:47.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you only have to look\nat the manual when you get stuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:51.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong about that.\NThis is the problem with techies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:57.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:00.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:01.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:07.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here...line 3, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:11.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:18.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, you're not going\nto play that flute, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:21.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Midgard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:24.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But your fate was always deletion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:27.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, let me just explain myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:32.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Curses! I won't let you\nget away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:39.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I pray for the salvation\nof their souls...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:55.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...I'm getting sucked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:58.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to...I've got\nto transfer myself over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:04.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:10.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:19.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:22.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:25.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi! Keiichi, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:36.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we'd better get out\nof here before someone comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:45.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take a look at this horrific sight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:59.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Due to an explosion of unknown origin\nthat occurred just before dawn...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:02.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the area around Yokohama Bay\nhas been completely destroyed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:05.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really, they're making\nsuch a big deal out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can you blame them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:09.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have time to put\neverything back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:12.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go tidy up properly\nlater on, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:14.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:18.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:21.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't yet died, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:25.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:39.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This body now belongs\nto the Lord of Terror...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:42.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and Midgard's flute\nis now in my clutches!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:46.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There is no longer anything\nyou goddesses can do to stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:51.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:56.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:59.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, attack me from any direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:10:00.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:02.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:03.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:06.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have to take Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:10.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you infect me\ninstead, Lord of Terror?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:23.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:28.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's about to descend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:29.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:59.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to kill my hostage\nalong with me? Almighty One?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:06.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who ever thought one the Battle Wings\nwould descend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:09.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:17.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was ordered by Yggdrasil to\nannihilate the Lord of Terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:20.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot risk allowing the demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:24.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to take over this world, just\nto save the life of one human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:26.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to put an end to this struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:35.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you go on the offensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:43.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really believe you\ncan parry my attack forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:50.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Sister!{\i0}\NBelldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:57.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:12:02.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what it takes...\nI will protect Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:05.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that you'll even\ndefy an order from Yggdrasil?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:09.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means losing my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:11.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:15.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I take it there'll be\nno changing your mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:21.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:30.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:35.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him...his mind's been\ntaken over, yet he still resists!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:47.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think I understand now\nwhat makes you stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:48.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:54.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case, I'll just wait\nuntil the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:58.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the next time I'm summoned,\nI'm not going to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What could be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:09.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Almighty, send in your\NValkyries or whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:12.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because now I've got\nthe ultimate shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:15.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:19.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should find a new medium\nto transfer over to soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:23.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh! It's the Gate of\nthe Netherworld again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:25.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! The little squirt there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:31.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to make me\na 10-Dimensional Scythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:34.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And what are you going to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:39.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The chains that bind the Gate of the\NNetherworld are 10-dimensional, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:42.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you make it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:46.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because a seal made by the gods can\nonly be broken by an instrument...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...made by the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:49.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't want to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:51.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought you'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:53.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! One blow and he'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:58.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:03.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can\nuse to do my calculations?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:05.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:09.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it is a type\nof digital calculator...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:12.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So this gets carried over...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:16.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And this gets moved over here\nand this is the result!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:19.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And that means that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:21.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:26.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'm not supposed\nto be happy about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:34.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When all's said and done, she's just\nwallowing in the joy of creation again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:41.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:44.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:48.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, here's a question for you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:52.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After opening this gate,\nwhat am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:54.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to summon all the\ndemons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:57.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nice try! But you're only half-correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:15:01.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Humans and demons can\nnever co-exist, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:08.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I shall turn this world into a\nparadise for demons and reign as king!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:09.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:11.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What about the people on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:15.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have no use for them,\nnot in my world, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:18.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy! We have no choice now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:21.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:25.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:29.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but we can't pick Keiichi over\nthe rest of the world, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:34.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all over if he cuts the chains!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:41.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:46.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then! I'm gonna\nstart cutting! Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:55.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! I can't bring myself to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:15:59.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:05.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From here on in, I'm\ngoing to rule this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:10.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:13.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:17.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take Keiichi's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:20.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So please, let Keiichi go free!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:22.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:25.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy, get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:28.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I kill the Lord of Terror, the Gate\nof the Netherworld will disappear, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:31.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what happens to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:33.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just save Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:36.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, you've got to just save Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:39.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's what I was after all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:44.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After all, a human body is no\nvessel for the Lord of Terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:54.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lind...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:17:00.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Once he's possessed me, I want you\nto annihilate me along with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:08.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep my promise to you\nanymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:11.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:16.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:17.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:22.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something's repelling\nthe Lord of Terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:23.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:29.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see...since they're based on different\npulses, he can't infect a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:31.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:36.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mean I can't transfer\nmyself to her body?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:39.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate,\nI'm going to lose the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:41.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to find another medium!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:53.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is what they mean by\N''A sight for the gods!''{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:59.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad that I got to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:04.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget you, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:11.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:13.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:14.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Lord of Terror has severed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:21.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi's going to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:33.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:35.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:40.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy...Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:45.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The question now is how am I going to\ntransfer to the ne{\i0}xt {\i1}host.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:49.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey! What the hell are you doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:51.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can't ever escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:53.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:55.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:19:00.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you subject a disk to a powerful\nmagnetic force, it'll erase all the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:02.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You...you wouldn't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:05.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:10.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No! Please don't erase me! Help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:20.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Am I home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:23.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What am I doing wearing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:27.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm responsible for allowing\nthe seal to be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:30.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The seal was broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:33.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, regardless of the outcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:36.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the fact remains that you\ndid destroy the Lord of Terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:42.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing is...since the main\nsystem is still down and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:46.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the subsystem is running both in safe\nmode and as proxy for the seal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:50.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...all of Yggdrasil's functions\nhave more or less been halted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:52.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:53.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:57.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To all intents and purposes, all duties\npertaining to goddess contracts...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:20:00.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and all records of\nwork-related penalties...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:03.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...all of the aforementioned\nhave been erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:07.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding! You mean my license\nsuspension's out the window, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:10.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't anything to be glad about!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:13.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I have to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:18.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You may either escape under your\nown power, or else remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:20.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to leave it up to you to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:22.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:25.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that Belldandy's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:28.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:32.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lind, I wish you wouldn't be\nin such a hurry to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:39.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I may be a Combat Specialist,\nbut I don't want to be insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:43.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:46.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:51.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Big Sister's going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:55.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's a question we probably\ndon't even need to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:20:59.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Was she one of those Valkyries\nyou told me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:03.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was Lind...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:05.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We owe her our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.19,0:21:09.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So...uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:13.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What about the contract being voided?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:14.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:19.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because the contract you and I\nsigned has been voided...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:23.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that means that I no longer\nhave a duty to fulfill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:25.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:28.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:31.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going back to Heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:32.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:37.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the contract\nhas been voided.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:43.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you see...that's not the only\nreason I've stayed here until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:44.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:48.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You showed me, a goddess, how\nwonderful it is to live as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:53.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And you also taught me about\nfeelings that I've never felt before!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:22:00.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've decided to stay on here,\neven if the contract no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:02.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:06.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:16.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me a lot, too...\nand I'm really grateful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.05,0:22:18.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.82,0:22:20.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...from here on in...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:24.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I want you to always be by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:37.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day when I woke up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:49.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A day like any other...\nanother one just beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.25,0:22:58.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There you are, yawning...\nyour face is still so sleepy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:05.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because each peaceful day\nwe share is a miracle to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:12.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is where my heart\nwill always return...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.01,0:23:14.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:20.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's only one thing I wish for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:27.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I chase after the same dream,\nwherever it may go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:33.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The love I feel for you\ngives me strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.23,0:23:39.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May tomorrow be as joyful as today...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.47,0:23:44.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my wish...{\i0}
